      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.ammaar-muslim": [
          "9. [9/17] al-Kafi: Muhammad b. Ismail from al-Fadhl b. Shadhan from Ibn Abi Umayr from Jamil b. Salih from Aban b. Taghlib from Abi Abdillah عليه السلام who said: I would have even liked it that my companions’ heads are lashed with whips for them to gain a comprehensive understanding (of the religion)."
        ]
      }
